		"UIName": "P.A.M.",
		"Id": "Gear_PAM",
		"Name": "Pirate-Accelerated Myomer",
		"Details": "Pirates have one mission: get in, get the loot, get out quickly. In that vein, the pirates of the Oberon Confederation developed their own take on Myomer Acceleration Signal Circuitry (or M.A.S.C.). Calling it P.A.M., or Pirate-Accelerated Myomer, the gear works on a similar principle as M.A.S.C. where an electrical signal stimulates the myomer to accelerate the 'Mech to faster speeds. However, unlike M.A.S.C., P.A.M. is triggered manually and has stacking effects over time. Also unlike M.A.S.C., P.A.M. can fail catastrophically if overused, eventually damaging or even destroying the 'Mech carrying the gear. <b><color=#099ff2>Automatically activated, works continuously.</color></b>",
		"Icon": "muscular-torso"
